Package: ANNt
Type: Package
Title: Artificial Neural Network with 't' Distribution Portfolio
Version: 1.1.1
Date: 2023-10-07
Authors: Alexandre Silva de Oliveira and Paulo Sergio Ceretta
Maintainer: The package maintainer <aleoli05@gmail.com> <ceretta10@gmail.com>
Description: Portfolio optimization system using Artificial Neural Networks. 
    ANNt uses a Perceptron architecture, with a hidden layer of size equal to the number of information in the input neurons. Classifies the output neurons of assets with leptokurtic distribution, which is more appropriate for financial data.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
Imports: quantmod, PerformanceAnalytics, magrittr, fBasics, tidyverse, stringr,
    dplyr, neuralnet, zoo, forecast, timetk, moments, data.table, ggplot2, rvest,
    caret, readxl, writexl, portfolio.optimization, PortfolioAnalytics, ROI, 
    fPortfolio, timeSeries, gridExtra, cowplot, portfolioBacktest, CVXR, MFDFA,
    DEoptim, rvest, cvar, IntroCompFinR
Collation: Please cite as: OLIVEIRA, A. S.; CERETTA, P. S. ANNt Package for R. https://github.com/ANNt  
